OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with patchy rain across
OL,6,Fthe region from early morning.
OL,7,FGradually turning brighter with sunny
OL,8,Fspells developing from the north.
OL,9,FBecoming increasingly blustery into
OL,10,Fthe afternoon with scattered showers
OL,11,Fpossible, especially later near to the
OL,12,Fcoast. Chillier than of late.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers returning through the
OL,15,Fnight, which could turn heavy at times
OL,16,Fduring the early morning especially.
OL,17,FWinds increasing around coastal areas,
OL,18,Fbut a slight frost developing in
OL,19,Fsheltered inland spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
