OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother day of sunshine and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,7,Fagain could be heavy with the added
OL,8,Frisk of hail in places. Remaining
OL,9,Fchilly, with temperatures below
OL,10,Faverage.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FStaying mixed to end the week with
OL,14,Ffurther sunshine and showers likely.
OL,15,FDrier, with lighter winds to start the
OL,16,Fweekend though. Temperatures staying
OL,17,Fbelow average for the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
